asset.hookText:
The world's first combination of facial epilator and cleansing brush.
It is 6x better than manual cleansing and also removes even the finest hairs for up to 4 weeks of smooth skin, leaving you with a perfect canvas, so you can decide whether to go nude, or just start your make-up from a great foundation. It removes make-up, oils, pollutants, and impurities and is great if you are looking for a solution to get rid of blackheads.
